CSS Pseudo-elements
应用：
72）make the first letter special in a text
73) make the first line special in a text
74) make the first letter and first line special
75) use:before to insert some content before an element
76) use:after to insert some content after an element

CSS Navigation Bars
应用：
77）fully styled vertical navigation bar
78) fully styled horizontal navigation bar ( li {float:left;} )

CSS Image Gallery
79) image gallery

CSS Image Opacity
80) creating transparent images - mouseover effect
81) creating a transparent box with text on a background image

CSS Image Sprites
82) An image sprite
83) An image sprite - a navigation list
84) An image sprite with hover effect

CSS Attribute Selectors
85）select elements with a title attribute
86) select elements with title=a specify value
87) select elements with title=a specify value（even if the attribute has space-separated values)
88) select elements with title=a specify value (even if the attribute has hyphen-separated values)

